        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-11-14 14:44:19.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: -Code-Review\n\nThanks Dan for pointing out. @Janani I think we can use \"_\" as a delimiter between module name and data node, as standard YANG module names doesn't have it. With this we needn't have to change the ANTLR grammar.",
        "patchset_number": 1
